---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
    title="About · Jonathan Ortega"
    description="About Jonathan Ortega, software engineer focused on resilient systems and durable software design."
>
    <section class="bg-canvas">
        <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-300 px-8 pt-40 pb-20">
            <p
                class="mb-8 font-mono text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-accent-green"
            >
                About
            </p>

            <h1
                class="m-0 mb-10 max-w-[16ch] font-mono text-[clamp(2.75rem,8vw,6.5rem)] font-bold leading-none tracking-[-0.04em] text-ink"
            >
                Building software
                <br />
                <span class="text-ink-muted">that lasts</span>
            </h1>

            <div
                class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 border-t border-line pt-10 md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_minmax(0,1fr)] md:gap-16"
            >
                <div>
                    <p
                        class="mb-5 max-w-[52ch] font-sans text-base leading-relaxed font-light text-ink-muted"
                    >
                        I design and build systems that stay understandable
                        under pressure. Most of my day-to-day work sits at the
                        intersection of TypeScript, React, and backend
                        infrastructure, where reliability and clarity matter
                        more than novelty.
                    </p>

                    <p
                        class="m-0 max-w-[52ch] font-sans text-base leading-relaxed font-light text-ink-muted"
                    >
                        This site is my working notebook: a place for essays,
                        notes, and snippets that capture decisions while they
                        are still fresh.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <p
                        class="mb-4 font-mono text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-faint"
                    >
                        Areas of focus
                    </p>

                    <ul class="m-0 flex list-none flex-col gap-2 p-0">
                        <li
                            class="flex items-start gap-2 font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed font-light text-ink-muted"
                        >
                            <span
                                class="mt-[0.55rem] inline-block h-1 w-1 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent-green"
                            ></span>
                            TypeScript architecture for long-lived codebases.
                        </li>
                        <li
                            class="flex items-start gap-2 font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed font-light text-ink-muted"
                        >
                            <span
                                class="mt-[0.55rem] inline-block h-1 w-1 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent-green"
                            ></span>
                            UI systems with clear information hierarchy.
                        </li>
                        <li
                            class="flex items-start gap-2 font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed font-light text-ink-muted"
                        >
                            <span
                                class="mt-[0.55rem] inline-block h-1 w-1 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent-green"
                            ></span>
                            Operational tooling that reduces decision fatigue.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
